.. code-block:: pascal

    function TRSBankScreen.getPackCountDTM(dtm: integer): integer;

Searches for the dtm in each bankscreen pack slot and will return how many matches it finds.

.. note::

    - by Olly
    - Last Updated: 02 January 2013 by Ashaman88

Example:

.. code-block:: pascal

    var
      dtm: integer;
      i: integer;
